Interface SignalView.Listener<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Reactor.RListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Slot, UnitSlot
    Enclosing interface:
    SignalView<T>

    public static interface SignalView.Listener<T>
extends Reactor.RListener
    Used to observe events from a signal. Normally one uses Slot rather than this listener, but this interface exists to allow Java 8 lambdas to be used as well.
